specifically to protest the arrests of 50 laborers at an
intersection last Thursday. Houchin did not permit the demonstrators
inside, but said the letter would be delivered to one of Gates'
representatives.
   Sheen, 48, has participated in numerous anti-nuclear protests and
demonstrations on other issues.
