and killing of Merle Yurdira Mondain. He confessed to keeping the
girl tied to his bed for two days while he drugged and raped her.
   He and his teen-age houseboy, who remains in jail, told the court
they later strangled the 6-year-old and dumped the body in a
junkyard. The houseboy testified that Alejandro Braun was addicted
to drugs and alcohol.
