Detroit 33 snow; Miami 75 fair; New York 43 rain; Philadelphia 40
drizzle; Pittsburgh 45 rain; Portland, Maine 34 cloudy; Washington
39 drizzle.
   _Central: Bismarck 11 fair; Chicago 29 snow; Dallas-Fort Worth 45
cloudy; Denver 26 partly cloudy; Des Moines 22 snow; Indianapolis 37
foggy; Kansas City 26 snow; Minneapolis-St. Paul 16 cloudy;
Nashville 55 rain; New Orleans 71 cloudy; St. Louis 32 foggy.
