fair; Los Angeles 52 foggy; Phoenix 61 fair; Salt Lake City 32
partly cloudy; San Diego 54 fair; San Francisco 52 partly cloudy;
Seattle 43 fair.
   _Canada: Montreal 30 foggy; Toronto 32 snow.
