<HEAD>For release Thursday, Feb. 23, and thereafter</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: This is the Explorations package for Feb. 23 in summary form.</HEAD>
<HEAD>Nose Research Provides Route to Wider Knowledge</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BOSTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
